#: ../../doc/invoke.rst:52
msgid ""
"The ``script_invoke`` also supports invoking a method, a.k.a., member "
"function. You need to put the script object in front of the script "
"function pointer in arguments. This is designed to simulate a method call"
" ``obj.method()``."
msgstr ""
"``script_invoke`` 还支持调用方法（即成员函数）。"
"你需要在参数中将脚本对象放在脚本函数指针之前。"
"这样设计是为了模拟方法调用 ``obj.method()``。"

#: ../../doc/invoke.rst:56
msgid ""
"The type of script object can be either ``(const) void*`` or a type that "
"can be cast into ``(const) asIScriptObject*``."
msgstr ""
"脚本对象的类型可以是 ``(const) void*``，"
"也可以是能转换为 ``(const) asIScriptObject*`` 的类型。"

